<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Ventral idiosoma showing the sternometasternal, genitiventrianal and parapodal shield. A Holotype of Krantzolaspina angustatus B Paratype of Indutolaelaps jiroftensis syn. nov., photos by Raphael Castilho C New material from Indonesia." , "Figure 4. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female, Gnathosomal structures. Holotype (Left); Indutolaelaps jiroftensis syn. nov. (Middle), photos by Raphael Castilho; New material from Indonesia (Right). A-C Subcapitulum D-F Epistome G-I Chelicera J-L Palp trochanter with a ventral spine-like process." , "Figure 2. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Ventral idiosoma." , "Figure 5. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Palp, note the ventral spine-like process in palptrochanter." , "Figure 6. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. A-D Legs I-IV, respectively. Coxae I-IV in the Fig. 2." , "Figure 1. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Dorsal idiosoma." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479381" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479384" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479385" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479382" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479386" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479383" .

